        "title": "Poème d'Halloween",
        "description": "Poème d'Halloween",
        "content": "<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Automne</h2><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Rouge, jaune, orange,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Ces couleurs dominent alors que la saison change.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">C’est le temps des citrouilles, des costumes, des <i>Pumpkin\nSpice Latte</i>,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Les coffres enflent de cet argent dépensé.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">L’embrasement des forêts,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Présage l’arrivée prochaine de l’hiver,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Précède le brun morne de transition,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Offre à la nature le dernier gala de l’année,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Avant que de blanc tout soit vêtu.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj54_yTbQblV8Y6ovWSFizSFXkfxhqGWYBYCuIhZwIZ-QBTLYfX77qWjOJIUMwRrrmI6Kwoc89VP9Q7lNipI6zB1H1Anf4ptcqbfJZFM-n61iB4wHTsB1PVwELjBEX6prxDK6NACM_Hz8uZ1Lt4jE2QQKAh-BDLt__z4AKxnitlss7jyjRBOQoGJz6pXS_d/s922/745548.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"615\" data-original-width=\"922\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj54_yTbQblV8Y6ovWSFizSFXkfxhqGWYBYCuIhZwIZ-QBTLYfX77qWjOJIUMwRrrmI6Kwoc89VP9Q7lNipI6zB1H1Anf4ptcqbfJZFM-n61iB4wHTsB1PVwELjBEX6prxDK6NACM_Hz8uZ1Lt4jE2QQKAh-BDLt__z4AKxnitlss7jyjRBOQoGJz6pXS_d/w640-h426/745548.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div><br /><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\"><br /></span><p></p></div><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Le peuple enchaîné</h2><div><p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><v:shapetype coordsize=\"21600,21600\" filled=\"f\" id=\"_x0000_t75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" o:spt=\"75\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" stroked=\"f\">\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\">\n <v:formulas>\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\">\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\">\n </v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas>\n <v:path gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" o:extrusionok=\"f\">\n <o:lock aspectratio=\"t\" v:ext=\"edit\">\n</o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape alt=\"Une image contenant Feuille d’érable, érable, automne, feuille\n\nDescription générée automatiquement\" id=\"Image_x0020_18\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s1026\" style=\"height: 195.8pt; left: 0; margin-left: -95.3pt; margin-top: 16.1pt; mso-height-percent: 0; mso-height-percent: 0; mso-height-relative: margin; mso-position-horizontal-relative: text; mso-position-horizontal: absolute; mso-position-vertical-relative: text; mso-position-vertical: absolute; mso-width-percent: 0; mso-width-percent: 0; mso-width-relative: margin; mso-wrap-distance-bottom: 0; mso-wrap-distance-left: 9pt; mso-wrap-distance-right: 9pt; mso-wrap-distance-top: 0; mso-wrap-style: square; position: absolute; text-align: left; visibility: visible; width: 195.8pt; z-index: 251780096;\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\">\n <v:imagedata o:title=\"Une image contenant Feuille d’érable, érable, automne, feuille\n\nDescription générée automatiquement\" src=\"file:///C:/Users/charl/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/15/clip_image001.png\">\n</v:imagedata></v:shape><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">En cette soirée hantée,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Circule dans\nles quartiers un peuple déguisé,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Les enfants\nmignons et ceux apeurant,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Défilent aux\nportes allégrement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Que vous\ncélébriez cette fête ou pas,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Nous sommes\ntous déguisés, a-ha !<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">En prisonniers\nmalgré nous,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Avec le\ncapitalisme comme gardien de cellule,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Victimes de\nl’attrait du sucré,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span lang=\"FR\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;\">Condamnés à\nperpétuité.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\">Luz Germain-Lumagbas</div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><i style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px;\">***Texte provenant de la première édition de l'Éco de l'Île imprimé</i></div>"
